sequenceDiagram
    participant Engine as IndicatorExecutionEngine
    participant Deps as Dependency outputs
    participant Indicator as Indicator instance
    participant Decision as Decision layer
    participant Projection as BotLens / chart / debug

    Engine->>Deps: resolve OutputRef inputs
    Engine->>Indicator: apply_bar(bar, inputs)
    Indicator-->>Engine: mutate private state
    Engine->>Indicator: snapshot()
    Indicator-->>Engine: RuntimeOutput entries
    Engine->>Indicator: overlay_snapshot() when requested
    Indicator-->>Engine: RuntimeOverlay entries
    Engine->>Indicator: detail_snapshot() when requested
    Indicator-->>Engine: RuntimeDetail entries
    Engine->>Decision: typed outputs only
    Engine->>Projection: overlays/details as projections

    Note over Decision,Projection: Projection surfaces are not strategy inputs.
